									"patching_rect" : [ 10.0, 346.0, 246.0, 86.0 ],
									"text" : "Note that once you measure your computer's latency, you can connect other equipment in the loop from output to input and calculate its latency. How much is that Firewire interface slowing you down? How much does the I/O vector size really matter?"
